<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.9.11">
<l>ēṟkum perumpukaḻ vāṉava ricaṉkaṇ ṇaṉṟaṉak</l>
<l>kēṟkum perumpukaḻ vaṇkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉcol</l>
<l>lēṟkum perumpuka ḻāyirat tuḷḷivaiyu mōrpat</l>
<l>tēṟkum perumpukaḻ collaval lārkkillai caṉmamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To those who master speaking the great fame that is suitable</l>
<l>of these ten among the thousand of great praise that is suitable</l>
<l>composed by Caṭakōpaṉ of liberal Kurukūr of great praise that is suitable</l>
<l>for Kṛṣṇa, the lord of the celestials of great fame that is suitable.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
